<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_Redirector::setGoto</p>

<p>rewrite the array $params in a sequence of /param/value</p>

<p>but when you provide an array in value, it's not converted in multiple params, like this ?param[]=value1&amp;param[]=value2
but in param/array</p>

<p>And in th same way, provide a solution for rewriting parameters including "/".
In example a date 23/11/1982 become param/23/11/1982 , and 11 its become the name of the second parameter and 1982 the value.</p>

<p>we also provided the same solution ?param=23/11/1982</p>

<p>almost, we can use a option for choosing type of rewrite parameters</p>

